, \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following FIFA's decision, the reigning Olympic champions will drop to minus three points in Group A, with two matches left to play and a mountain to climb if they are to move past the group stage.\", \"from\": 1162, \"to\": 1359, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1172, \"end\": 1176, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999954170562, \"rank\": 4.526293134276259e-09, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}, {\"begin\": 1255, \"end\": 1262, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\", \"score\": 0.970737665994802, \"rank\": 0.030059968825846932, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision remains subject to a potential appeal to the Court of Arbitration for Sport.\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1450, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We feel terrible for the athletes on the Canadian Women's Olympic soccer team who as far as we understand played no role in this matter,\\\" said David Shoemaker, CEO and Secretary General of the Canadian Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 1452, \"to\": 1673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1494, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9967433968316364, \"rank\": 0.003154868970599479, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}, {\"begin\": 1646, \"end\": 1672, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In support of the athletes, together with Canada Soccer, we are exploring rights of appeal related to the six point deduction at this Olympic tournament.\\\"\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1830, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1718, \"end\": 1731, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canada Soccer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada Soccer CEO and General Secretary, Kevin Blue, described the FIFA decision as \\\"excessively punitive\\\" towards the players.\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1832, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canada Soccer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1903, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"score\": 0.9999999954170562, \"rank\": 4.526293134276259e-09, \"text\": \"FIFA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FIFA\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canada are scheduled to play France, who top Group A on three points, on Sunday.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2041, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1961, \"end\": 1967, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4020104389966974e-14, \"text\": \"Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1990, \"end\": 1996, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9948634410013342, \"rank\": 0.00515270431339254, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2006, \"end\": 2013, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\", \"score\": 0.970737665994802, \"rank\": 0.030059968825846932, \"text\": \"Group A\", \"types\": [\"Q500834\", \"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2018_AFF_Championship\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They then take on Colombia, who like New Zealand have no points, on Wednesday.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2060, \"end\": 2068, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9624897476870056, \"rank\": 0.038972100191517485, \"text\": \"Colombia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Colombia_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9998681534380276, \"rank\": 0.00013163187464341157, \"text\": \"New Zealand\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Zealand_women's_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The top two teams in each group and the two best third-ranked teams qualify for the Olympic quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 2122, \"to\": 2229, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The incident caused Priestman and the other officials involved to be suspended by Canada Soccer, the sport's national governing body, and sent home from the Games.\", \"from\": 2231, \"to\": 2394, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2313, \"end\": 2326, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canada Soccer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Canadian Olympic Committee removed Priestman on Thursday after her suspension by Canada Soccer.\", \"from\": 2396, \"to\": 2495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2400, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 2481, \"end\": 2494, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canada Soccer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assistant Andy Spence will coach Canada for the remainder of the Games.\", \"from\": 2496, \"to\": 2567, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2517, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Spence\", \"score\": 0.9999899697693844, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Andy Spence\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q628099\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Spence\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Spence\"}, {\"begin\": 2523, \"end\": 2535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coach_Canada\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"coach Canada\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coach_Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Coach_Canada\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Priestman apologized on Wednesday for what had happened and said ultimate responsibility lay with her.\", \"from\": 2569, \"to\": 2671, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This does not represent the values that our team stands for,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2672, \"to\": 2744, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Priestman, 38, who had previously worked as women's Development Officer for England's Football Association, extended her contract in January through the 2027 Women's World Cup, having earned praise from Canada Soccer for her \\\"pivotal part\\\" in the development of the women's program.\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 3028, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2949, \"end\": 2962, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canada Soccer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a job advertisement on Canada Soccer's website in January, the women's national team said it was seeking a performance analyst who was \\\"able to operate drone\\\" and a \\\"working knowledge of managing training camera is preferred.\\\"\", \"from\": 3030, \"to\": 3259, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3056, \"end\": 3069, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canada Soccer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Canadian sports network TSN reported that drone use predates the 2024 Olympics, with sources telling the network the team had also filmed other opponents' training, including at the previous Olympic tournament in 2021.\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3479, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3261, \"end\": 3269, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"score\": 0.9967433968316364, \"rank\": 0.003154868970599479, \"text\": \"Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was no immediate comment from Canada Soccer or the Canadian Olympic Committee.\", \"from\": 3481, \"to\": 3565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3517, \"end\": 3530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canada Soccer\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Soccer_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 3538, \"end\": 3564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Canadian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canadian_Olympic_Committee\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday, former Canadian national team players Christine Sinclair and Stephanie Labbe said players had never been shown drone footage during their time on the team.\", \"from\": 3567, \"to\": 3733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3585, \"end\": 3607, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2725633085366343e-14, \"text\": \"Canadian national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 3616, \"end\": 3634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Sinclair\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Christine Sinclair\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Sinclair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christine_Sinclair\"}, {\"begin\": 3639, \"end\": 3654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Labb\\u00e9\", \"score\": 0.999999639680092, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stephanie Labbe\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Labb\\u00e9\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephanie_Labb\\u00e9\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Kaylyn Kyle, former national team player who competed at the 2012 London Olympics, said players were now paying the price for other people's actions.\", \"from\": 3735, \"to\": 3884, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3735, \"end\": 3746, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylyn_Kyle\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaylyn Kyle\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylyn_Kyle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaylyn_Kyle\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Only the players suffer for stupidity and selfishness.\", \"from\": 3886, \"to\": 3941, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The amount of work that goes into prep for an OG's (Olympic Games) to only have their dreams and hopes shattered,\\\" she said on X.- Rappler.com  How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 4114, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3988, \"end\": 3990, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Own_goal\", \"score\": 0.9999999999590727, \"rank\": 4.0729394209278314e-11, \"text\": \"OG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Own_goal\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Own_goal\"}, {\"begin\": 4073, \"end\": 4084, \"title\